reviewText:
Can not play on any DVD player.....I have tried numerous times and nothing will play.
This purchase is completely not useful to me or anyone else...it was a gift and now
a complete embarrassment. Not too say how upset I am over this.  I hope and pray you could rectify
this problem and send positive feedback.  I await your reply.
Be aware, this is a UK release and will not play on standard equipment and has subtitles.
